com.nuvoex.fileuploader

Class UploadBroadcastReceiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      • com.nuvoex.fileuploader.UploadBroadcastReceiver

  • public abstract class UploadBroadcastReceiver
extends BroadcastReceiver
    A BroadcastReceiver that receives file upload actions and calls the appropriate methods. Applications should implement the abstract methods for responding to various upload events. This BroadcastReceiver must be registered in the manifest with the proper intent filter. 
         
     <receiver android:name=".UploadBroadcastReceiverSubclass">
          <intent-filter>
              <action android:name="com.nuvoex.fileuploader.ACTION_STATUS_CHANGE" />
              <category android:name="app.package.name.CATEGORY_UPLOAD" />
          </intent-filter>
     </receiver>
    Replace app.package.name with the correct application package name.
